			<title><![CDATA[Question About Japan's House Manufacturing Culture]]></title>
			<link>http://www.graffe.com/forums/showthread.php?78398-Question-About-Japan-s-House-Manufacturing-Culture&amp;goto=newpost</link>
			<pubDate>Sat, 16 Jan 2016 15:07:03 GMT</pubDate>
			<description>According to Wikipedia (https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Housing_in_Japan), Japan makes shit houses on purpose. Now, the US generally makes houses in a manner that is nonsensical, but they are not purposefully wasting resources generally. This seems extremely contradictory to the rest of Japanese...</description>
